\c 2
\p
\s Vapristi vanotukwa naJehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino imwi vapristi, chinzwai uyu murairo unouya kwamuri.
\v 2 Kana imwi musingadi kunzwa, kana musingadi kuita nomwoyo wenyu zvandakaraira kuti mukudze zita rangu ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo ipapo ndichatuma kutuka pamusoro penyu, ndichatuka ropafadzo dzenyu; zvirokwazvo ndatozvituka, nekuti hamuzviiti nomwoyo wenyu.
\v 3 Tarirai, ndichatuka vana venyu, ndichanamira ndove kuzviso zvenyu, iyo ndove yemitambo yenyu; muchabviswa pamwechete naro.
\v 4 Ipapo muchaziva kuti ndini ndakakutumirai murairo uyu, kuti sungano yangu ive naRevhi ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo.
\v 5 Sungano yangu navo yakange iri youpenyu norugare; ndakavapa izvo kuti vanditye, vakanditya, vakadedera nokuda kwezita rangu.
\v 6 Murairo wezvokwadi wakange uri mumuromo wavo, kusarurama hakuna kuwanikwa pamiromo yavo; vakafambidzana neni norugare nokururama, vakadzora vazhinji pazvakaipa.
\v 7 nekuti miromo yomupristi inofanira kuchengeta zivo, vanhu vanofanira kubvunza murairo pamusoro wake; nekuti ndiye nhume yaJehovha wehondo.
\v 8 Asi imwi makatsauka panzira; makagumbusa vazhinji pamurayiro; makasvibisa sungano yaRevhi ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo.
\v 9 Saka ndakakuitai vanhu vanozvidzwa navanorambwa navanhu vaose, zvamusina kuchengeta nzira dzangu, mukatsaura vanhu pakutonga murayiro.
\v 10 Ko isu tose hatina baba vamwe here? haasi Mwari umwe  wakatisika here? Tinogonyengerana neiko umwe  neumwe   hama yake, tichimhura sungano yamadzibaba edu?
\v 11 Judha vakanyengera, chinhu chinonyangadza chaitwa pakati palsiraeri napaJerusarema; nekuti Judha vakamhura nzvimbo tsvene yaJehovha, inodikanwa naye, vakawana mukunda wamwari wavatorwa.
\v 12 Munhu anoita zvakadai, Jehovha achamubvisira pamatende aJakove, anodana neanopindura, neanovigira Jehovha wehondo zvipiriso
\v 13 Munoitawo izvozvi munofukidza atari yaJehovha nemisodzi, nokuchema, nokugomera, naizvozvo haacharangariri chipiriso, kana kuchigamuchira nomufaro pamaoko enyu.
\v 14 Kunyange zvakadaro munoti, Nemhaka yeiko? nekuti Jehovha akange ari chapupu pakati pako nomukadzi woujaya hwako, wawakanyengera, kunyange ari shamwari yako, nomukadzi wako wawakaita sungano yako naye.
\v 15 Ko haana kuita umwe  chete, kunyange akange ane umwe  Mweya wakasara here? Zvino wakaitireiko umwe  chete? Wakatsvaka rudzi rwaMwari. Saka chenjererai mweya yenyu, kurege kuva neumwe   anonyengera mukadzi woujaya hwake.
\v 16 nekuti ndinovenga kurambana ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri uye munhu anofukidza nguwo yake nokumanikidza ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo; saka chenjererai mweya yenyu, kuti murege kunyengera.
\v 17 Makanetsa Jehovha namashoko enyu. Kunyange zvakadaro munoti, Takamunetsa neiko? Pakutaura kwenyu, muchiti, umwe  neumwe   anoita zvakaipa, vakanaka pamberi paJehovha, ndivo vaanofarira, kana: Mwari wezvakarurama aripiko?
